# Demo branch: a public, non-secret build flag (VITE_DEMO_MODE=true) so the
# static demo build works out of the box on Vercel without manual env config.
# Scoped to production/development modes only — NOT a bare .env — so it
# doesn't leak into vitest's "test" mode and break the real-backend unit tests.
!app/.env.production
